# Design System (HTML mockups)

Source of truth: @ai/rules/design/design-system.md

## Quick Rules

- Self-contained HTML: all CSS + JS embedded, no external local files
- CDN only: Google Fonts, Lucide Icons, Chart.js (when needed)
- Always wrap screen in phone frame (375×812px)
- Dark theme only — no light mode variants
- Use CSS variables from design-system — never hardcode hex colors
- Staggered `fadeUp` animation on all cards/list items on page load
- File name: kebab-case matching feature (e.g. `transactions-list.html`)
- Output location: `designs/screens/<screen-name>.html`
